<author>F. De Beouf, F. De Beouf</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mnk yạ rb tạ̉tynạ ạlḥyạẗ
 flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 ạ̉nt yạ rb ḥṣny sndy flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 frḥẗ qlby tạ̉ty mnk rby flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 wbạsmk ạ̉jd tẖqty flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 ạlqrạr- mjd lk yạ rb ạ̉nt ʿẓym
 mjd lkl ạ̉ʿmạlk mjd yạ rb yạ nṣrnạ
 ḥbk ygẖmr qlbnạ flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 2- ạ̉nt yạ rb tnyr lylnạ flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 nwr tḍy lkẖṭwạtnạ flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk
 wfy ạlqtạl ttẖbt ạ̉ydynạ flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk</lyrics>
<title>flykẖbr fmy btsbyḥk</title>
</song>